@25   = ~Girdle of Demon Combat: Xiphias was a young mage, who had chosen to study the conjuring of Demons. But however, before he was allowed to start the course, he was forced by the school to have this belt built, which offers a few basic but important protections from the demonic kind. How this belt got into the Dwarven Treasure Hold is unknown, and thoughts of evil demons within the cave you found this spring to mind.

