@46   = ~Gauntlets are armored gloves.  They can be made of leather, metal plates, or chain mail.  Every suit of armor is assumed to include gauntlets of an appropriate type.  Magical gauntlets tend to be finer, lighter, and more easily worn than normal varieties.~
@47   = ~Gauntlets of Time Stopping. These much sought after Gauntlets found their way to Loron's ownership as a gift from one of his followers. As to where they acquired these interesting gloves, no one is quite sure. 
