@54   = ~Letter~
@55   = ~Loron,
   I hope you received this on time, because I write with terrible news. Corpae has acquired a small group of followers and has therefore regained considerable power. He is after you, seeking revenge. It is only a matter of time before he is powerful enough to teleport straight to your home shrine and capture you, so I suggest you leave at once to Athkatla, where Corpae will not be able to use any magic due to the strict laws enforced by the Cowled Wizards. Should you need to return to your shrine, I suggest acquiring protection of a sort.

If you should need to seek refuge, I am currently residing in a small Inn near the City Gates.
Yours Sincerely,
              Ademoth~
